Most of the time we ride but

sake their flashy sports cars,
sleek sedans, rusty jalopies or
tiny import models and walk.


Walking is rated as one of the
best methods for stimulating cir

itation. Doctors and health ex-

get up, move outside and trudge
the walks or country lanes.


Having few minutes to walk
unless it helps me complete some

angular as before.


have another complaint to
